<div id="pf2c0d" class="pf w4e h233" data-page-no="2c0d"><div class="pc pc2c0d w4e h233"><div class="t m24b0 x55 h6f y2aa4 ff3 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE BLESSING OF DAILY STUDY </div><div class="t mf5 x73 h27 y290d ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The beauty and riches of the word have a transforming influence on </div><div class="t me5c x3e h27 y2359 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mind and character.&quot;—Christ&apos;s </div><div class="t m1476 x7d h16 y2359 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Object Lessons, </div><div class="t m57c x8c h27 y21bc ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 132. </div><div class="t m2f1 x73 h27 y1ea9 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;There is nothing more calculated to strengthen the intellect than the </div><div class="t m6a3 x3e h27 ycf4 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study of the Scriptures. No other book is so potent to elevate the thoughts, </div><div class="t m9b6 x3e h27 y13f0 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to give vigor to the faculties, as the broad, ennobling truths of the Bible. </div><div class="t m2d5 x3e h27 y13b9 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">If God&apos;s word were studied as it should be, men would have a breadth of </div><div class="t m152 x3e h27 y151e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mind, a nobility of character, and a stability of purpose rarely seen in </div><div class="t m67e x3e h27 y1503 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these </div><div class="t m770 x4e h16 y1503 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">times.&quot;—Steps to Christ, </div><div class="t m1627 x1b h27 y1503 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page go. </div><div class="t m362 x73 h27 y10b9 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The more you search the Scriptures with humble hearts, the greater will </div><div class="t m9c1 x3e h27 y1e07 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be your interest. . . . Every day you should learn something new from the </div><div class="t m79a x3e h16 ya10 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Scriptures.&quot;—Testimonies, vol. </div><div class="t m356 x3b h27 y13bd ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5, p. 266. </div><div class="t m15dc x6 h17d y1c